len.", "I 2030 er det tusen \u00e5r siden Olav Haraldsson falt i slaget p\u00e5 Stiklestad.", "- Jubileet i 2030 m\u00e5 bli en nasjonal markering, sier kulturminister Linda Hofstad Helleland."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|nordtrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "a3f3f11bc5911f686af61af33043fd6dc0ef2fb8eb76f4b1ac98a33ae1316f71"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-07-27T20:51:58.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Kulturminister Linda Hofstad Helleland sto i g\u00e5r for den offisielle \u00e5pningen av det 63. spelet p\u00e5 Stiklestad. \u2013 Dette er b\u00e5de nyskapende historieformidling og inspirerende teater, sa hun."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/nordtrondelag/article13097327.ece/inl0a2/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Spel%20publikum2.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/2b830d9d570a8496db40acbeabab701294efbe70.jpg?598ec2b1"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["4000 s\u00e5 premieren p\u00e5 Stiklestad-spelet -adressa.no", "Skaper verdier", "Stor interesse", "Nasjonalt ansvar"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "2b830d9d570a8496db40acbeabab701294efbe70"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "nordtrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["spel", "dype spor", "premiere", "kulturminister"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["gr\u00fcnerl\u00f8kka", "spelet", "heilag olav", "stiklestadamfiet", "ute"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["tr\u00f8ndelag", "oslo", "norge", "stiklest